description:
On today’s show, Emily is talking about independence in a relationship & the importance of establishing those boundaries with a new partner — and as always, answering your sex, dating, & relationship questions.   

She gives advice on what to do when you & your partner don’t see eye to eye on how much quality time to spend together, how to give a spectacular nipplegasm (because who doesn’t want that?), and how to unlock those masturbatory multiple orgasms during sex with a partner. Plus, a beginner’s breakdown to prostate play. 


Follow Emily on all social: @sexwithemily

For even more sex talk, tips, & tricks visit sexwithemily.com
